 * Top-level --skill <slug> tagger (decision gad-178 / phase 42.3-16).
 * Any `gad <cmd> --skill <slug>` invocation sets GAD_ACTIVE_SKILL in the
 * environment so the trace hook can stamp the emitted tool_use events
